StackOverflow 

dataset consists 3,370,528 samples through July 31st, 2012 to Au- gust 14, 2012. 
In our experiments, we randomly select 20, 000 question titles from 20 different tags.

Training and test data as Google search snippets

Traning data: 
    File: train.txt
    Size: 10,060 snippets
    
Test data:
    File: test.txt
    Size: 2,280 snippets

Format: 
    Each snippet on each line
    Each snippet consists of a list of words/terms plus a class label at the end

8 domains (class labels):
    Business
    Computers
    Culture-Arts-Entertainment
    Education-Science
    Engineering
    Health
    Politics-Society
    Sports
    
